author: The Current
description:
To celebrate The Current’s 20th Anniversary, The Current’s Live Sessions Vault unlocks never-before-seen live performance videos of bands and artists who have played in our iconic studio. 

Watch to see the full session of Hippo Campus, featuring previously unreleased footage, from when they visited The Current studio back in 2016, plus an interview by Andrea Swensson.

Songs Performed 
00:00:00 Souls
00.04.10 Interview PT 1
00:08:40 Violet
00:12:54 Interview PT 2
00:20:30 South

Musicians
Jake Luppen — vocals, guitar
Nathan Stocker — vocals, guitar
Zach Sutton — bass, vocals
Whistler Allen — drums

Credits
Host — Andrea Swensson
Engineer – Michael DeMark
Producer – Andrea Swensson
Visuals  – Nate Ryan
Digital Producer – Natalia Toledo
Graphics – Natalia Toledo

The Current’s Live Sessions Vault is supported by the Minnesota Orchestra, GS Motors, and Delta Dental of Minnesota Foundation.
